&lt;p&gt;Associate work will include, but is not limited to:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;u&gt;Ducera Growth Ventures Responsibilities:&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Supporting in the negotiation, structuring, and evaluation of investment transactions.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conducting deep business diligence, including leading calls with investment target management teams and their outside advisors/consultants.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Conducting industry research utilizing traditional finance softwares and Ducera network.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Preparing investment committee materials, other LP/Partner materials, and other ongoing portfolio management materials.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Executing complex financial analyses, including valuation models, detailed financial forecasts, investment structure alternatives, monetization alternatives, and others.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Guiding and assisting portfolio company management teams in executing post-investment value creation.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;&lt;u&gt;Mergers &amp;amp; Acquisition Responsibilities:&lt;/u&gt;&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Producing analyses and models on leveraged buyouts, discounted cash flows, mergers and acquisitions accretion and dilution, and multiple valuation.&lt;/li&gt;
